```plantuml
@startuml Spiderpig86_SmoresUnderflow

actor User
participant "Frontend (React)" as Frontend
participant "Nginx (Load Balancer)" as Nginx
participant "su-users (Auth)" as Users
participant "su-questions (Service)" as Questions
participant "su-answers (Service)" as Answers
participant "RabbitMQ" as RabbitMQ
participant "su-search (ElasticSearch)" as Search
participant "Redis (Cache)" as Redis
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB

User -> Frontend: Posts question
Frontend -> Nginx: HTTP POST /api/questions
Nginx -> Questions: Forward request
Questions -> RabbitMQ: Publish question (async)
RabbitMQ -> Questions: Consume message
Questions -> MongoDB: Store question
Questions -> Redis: Cache question
Questions -> Search: Index question
Questions --> Nginx: 201 Created
Nginx --> Frontend: Response
Frontend --> User: Confirmation

User -> Frontend: Searches questions
Frontend -> Nginx: HTTP GET /api/search?q=...
Nginx -> Search: Forward request
Search -> Redis: Check cache
alt Cache hit
    Redis --> Search: Return cached results
else Cache miss
    Search -> MongoDB: Query questions
    MongoDB --> Search: Return results
    Search -> Redis: Cache results
end
Search --> Nginx: 200 OK with results
Nginx --> Frontend: Response
Frontend --> User: Display results

User -> Frontend: Posts answer
Frontend -> Nginx: HTTP POST /api/answers
Nginx -> Answers: Forward request
Answers -> RabbitMQ: Publish answer (async)
RabbitMQ -> Answers: Consume message
Answers -> MongoDB: Store answer
Answers -> Redis: Cache answer
Answers -> Search: Index answer
Answers --> Nginx: 201 Created
Nginx --> Frontend: Response
Frontend --> User: Confirmation

@enduml
```